139	/**
140	 * Upload form.
141	 *
142	 * Visual
143	 * ------
144	 * The Augustus Prima Porta sculpture now lives as a half-page backdrop (see
145	 * UploadPage in app/(authed)/upload/page.tsx + SculptureBackdrop). This
146	 * component is just the form itself; the patron sculpture is the room
147	 * it sits in.
148	 *
149	 * Bulk upload
150	 * -----------
151	 * Drop (or pick) one file → the classic single-file UI with an
152	 * editable title. Drop 2+ files → a queue view: per-row status,
153	 * per-row progress bar while bytes are in flight, per-row error on
154	 * failure. Shared metadata (description, visibility, publish flag,
155	 * excerpt, byline) applies to every item in the batch; titles are
156	 * auto-derived from filenames and can be edited from /library after
157	 * ingest. Uploads run sequentially to keep progress legible and avoid
158	 * thrashing the prepare endpoint; status polling runs concurrently
159	 * once all bytes have landed.
